noctalia-shell — https://github.com/noctalia-dev/noctalia-shell

margo's desktop shell (mshell) reimplements a number of widgets and
interaction patterns first seen in noctalia-shell. noctalia is a
Quickshell (QML) project and mshell is GTK4/Rust, so this is a
cross-language reimplementation rather than copied source; where logic
was translated, it is covered by the notice below. noctalia is MIT, so
its only requirement is that this notice be preserved.

